Author: Alright#0419
Content:
on Windows, you can go to 
`Agama\resources\app\assets\bin\win64\`
delete the file there called "komodod.exe"
download komodod.exe from here https://github.com/KomodoPlatform/komodo/releases/tag/dev-multios-0.4.0a-labs
and put it in that folder
